item.title: What a Finish
item.description: from me The past few days really drove home how much of a break I need. That coupled with the growing pains of using Linux was what really shifted the last two months by a few gears. It did, though, have surprising benefits. Started a “Prusa Printer Challenge” for myself in 2023>> as a way of turning free content into a new tool for the business. The contests on Printables are fun incentives to create - and be creative.
